I really liked this reciped and it got great reviews from everyone who ate it. I did make some substitutions as I did not have all the ingredients. I did'nt have enough regular flour so I used 1 cup regular flour and 1 cup stoned ground flour which gave it a wonderful texture. Also instead of cloves I used allspice. I didn't have raisins so I used dried apricots which I chopped up. It was great and I will make it again. Everyone wanted the recipe.

